      • create

        public static org.openrdf.model.Literal create(boolean theValue)
        Create a boolean instance of a Literal. Returns one of the two instances of a boolean literal, true or false. If you're only using Stardog's ValueFactory, you could safely compare with ==, but these also interoperate with Sesame's Literals, so you're still better off using equals.
        Parameters:
        theValue - the literal value
        Returns:
        the literal
